name: metre
definition: SI standard unit of length

name: kilogram
definition: SI standard unit of mass

name: second
definition: SI standard unit of time

name: ampere
definition: SI standard unit  of electrical current

name: kelvin
definition: SI standard unit of thermodynamic temperature

name: mole
definition: SI standard unit of amount of substance

name: candela
definition: SI standard unit of luminous intensity

name: radian
definition: SI standard derived unit of angle

definition: SI standard derived unit of solid angle

definition: SI standard derived unit of frequency

name: newton
definition: SI standard derived unit of force, weight

name: watt

name: ohm

name: tesla

definition: SI standard derived unit of temperature relative to 273.15 K

name: lumen
definition: SI standard derived unit of luminous flux

name: lux

definition: SI standard derived unit of radioactivity (decays per unit time)

definition: SI standard derived unit of absorbed dose (of ionizing radiation) J/kg

name: katal
definition: SI standard derived unit of catalytic activity
